// stats, transfer history, news mentions, recruit ranks — into a
// scout's dossier with five sections: identity, trajectory, fit,
// take, watch-list. Always produces a usable response, even on thin
// data. Never returns "INSUFFICIENT DATA" as a UX dead-end. The
// integrity move is in the verdict tier, not in the writeup.
