                summary: 'Texas Tech QB Brendan Sorsby on indefinite leave of absence entering treatment for gambling addiction. NCAA investigating alleged betting history. Eligibility for 2026 season unknown.',
                key_phrases: ['Brendan Sorsby', 'Texas Tech', 'NCAA investigation', 'gambling'],
